The code of conduct for the Global Script project is the Global Script Pledge, version 1.0.

The Global Script Pledge 1.0 can be accessed at https://raw.githubusercontent.com/jonathancast/globalscript-pledge/1.0/PLEDGE.

The latest version of the Global Script Pledge is always available at https://raw.githubusercontent.com/jonathancast/globalscript-pledge/master/PLEDGE.

The Global Script Pledge may be updated, at the sole whim of the Global Script maintainer, to reflect changes or to make clarifications.
